entendes?

334
00:33:52,800 --> 00:33:54,200
Temos de fazê-lo.

335
00:33:54,500 --> 00:33:58,000
Temos de dar-lhe apoio incondicional.

336
00:34:00,100 --> 00:34:01,100
Ai temos?

337
00:34:01,300 --> 00:34:02,600
Sim.

338
00:34:04,400 --> 00:34:05,800
Eu é que preciso de apoio.

339
00:34:07,300 --> 00:34:08,800
Eu!

340
00:34:09,000 --> 00:34:10,900
A grávida com quase 40 anos

341
00:34:11,200 --> 00:34:12,900
